{
  "stem": "18654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 179.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember not going to school for a whole year in the afternoons, I only went in the mornings and I had to rest every afternoon.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These days that wouldn't happen, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in those days, they still did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to the local village school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The home, we were known as the Sun Ray girls and we-- we were always rather embarrassed because we had to wear red woolen pixie hoods, and we only were allowed to go out in groups.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't mix very much with local people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We weren't allowed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Saturdays and Sundays, we were locked out in the afternoons and told to go for walks so that matron could rest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know-- do you know I know so little about the war because we weren't allowed to listen to radios.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had radio, but we weren't allowed to listen to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was in her room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I know very little about the war except what I've learned since, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Perhaps it was just as well because it wasn't such happy news, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Newspapers, I don't think we ever read them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't have facilities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, we had very little money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We went-- I think I used to get some pocket money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think I used to get a shilling a week, of which I had to save sixpence and with of the sixpence I was-- I could buy perhaps some of my sweet ration or have my hair cut or go to the cinema, which they gave us a special rate.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think we used to spend three pennies-- old pennies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm talking about old money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
